Office hour
                                                                  pointers for assignment 1


                                                                
                                                                  

                                                                    

                                                                      

                                                                        

                                                                          
 1. Slide (PPT) format was chosen
                                                                            because TA wants sth concise. Do not have
                                                                            big block of texts. 


                                                                          
2. Make sure all the bullet points in the
                                                                            grading rubics are provided in your slide
                                                                          


                                                                          
3. definitely include a page that shows
                                                                            how your delivery of the final message looks
                                                                            like 


                                                                          
4. If you make assumptions, provide
                                                                            reasoning. 


                                                                          
5. Citations should be used if required.
                                                                            (you can pick your style as long as it is
                                                                            consistent)
